{"tid":669610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地男偷拍陪審團疑發相　官：無心之失","createTime":"2018-05-18T15:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T03:46:04.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e82019bf717b2a6832714832caee685a550c4cbf","tid":669610,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:10:33.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】旺角騷亂案審理中途，一名操普通話、自稱「內地遊客」年輕男子在庭內連環拍照拍片，包括對着陪審團方向，並以微信傳送出去。當被執達主任查問時，男子稱不熟悉香港法律，將內容刪除，執達主任既無報警，亦無留下男子資料就放行。至法官處理事件時，男子已失去蹤影。法官向陪審團稱估計男子只是「無心之失」，雖然相片已外傳，但「我哋唔知道佢拍攝咗乜嘢」，安撫陪審團「應該唔係針對各位」，毋須擔心。<br />\n法官彭寶琴（圖）在午休前先吩咐陪審團退席，再邀請目擊事件的女士出庭重述事件。她說留意到，當陪審團步出法庭時，該男子開啟電話拍攝功能，但知被她看見已收手。至控方傳召證人時，她再看到男子向陪審團方向拍了一張照片，並用微信將照片傳送出去。她遂通知庭內律師朋友，經法庭書記通知執達主任。"},{"pid":"4b6ac72fc3665c6703507cdbbaa85ef781f7f898","tid":669610,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"f89d1139169884f7bb95bbe975ccb8483f960b94","tid":669610,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6ac72fc3665c6703507cdbbaa85ef781f7f898","tid":669610,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ca1b7404e2891b1ad93a288e2943eaabde29f4","tid":669610,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c4701b36f0192b6120b2c13772c9bef16e98bad","tid":669610,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"有心定無意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a454ebbee77da30b23fb9bfbbaf984137e92f1","tid":669610,"uid":91633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:13:16.000Z","msg":"垃撚垃法官"},{"pid":"c91991c0c0dfae5bd0cb4d8c6aeb6855c88996f1","tid":669610,"uid":65406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:14:22.000Z","msg":"三權合作"},{"pid":"d8c30539510d28d1a55dd920d37eff3e8e7fe699","tid":669610,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd8431d4c3c7661480746001cf7395184a3b549","tid":669610,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:16:55.000Z","msg":"秋"},{"pid":"32559fc253732e483c58d986a5fd6db96e4d6dce","tid":669610,"uid":30647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"司法機構在拍照事件發生後，稱已將案件交給警方處理，但警方沒有拘捕任何人。<span style=\"color: red;\">審訊尾聲，在法官第二天引導陪審團時，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再有操普通話的男遊客在法庭外延伸部份拍照</span></span>。有熱心市民大叫「有人影相呀」，該男子即表現慌張。惟即使有大批保安和司法機構人員在場，但眾人只是「你眼望我眼」，數分鐘後才有保安走近該男子。此時他已將相片刪除，隨後司法機構人員才上前理解，將男子帶到一旁，但最終沒有報警或通知法庭，<span style=\"color: red;\">將男子放行</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180518/58208270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F58208270&d=8HhhJffOGWxBLVTaJGqiTxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ee705bea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F58208270&h=c55c9d11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180518/58208270</a><br />\n<br />\n原來 引導陪審團 果陣, 再有人影相, 捉到之後又係放人."},{"pid":"ae3048771ac85eaf10e8e8e69d719b9865b1a083","tid":669610,"uid":57410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"呢樣野唔用政治角度去睇 只係自欺欺人<br />\n正如普教中 仲有人討論普通話教中文 係咪對中文水平有幫助簡直係蒙在鼓裏既戇鳩一樣"},{"pid":"70c60126eb99cc840a44a91976b669322ea4a527","tid":669610,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:19:49.000Z","msg":"今日比人恐嚇 又話唔關事"},{"pid":"c3b2b3af243245c9f007e2427dda1155387dff3a","tid":669610,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T00:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509c959542e7ee60856f9eb2cebd0c8d7e4094d0","tid":669610,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T00:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飯民班撚樣即刻靜哂"},{"pid":"01155bd1db8fef205b4ed046640534f2b8a8eb46","tid":669610,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"10a9469902ae5787686183e0376fc1ca6f326d54","tid":669610,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T00:53:07.000Z","msg":"如果係影控方證人即刻判藐視法庭"},{"pid":"0efaa009d60cbdb0dccffbec4a8ab9872ae1dfcb","tid":669610,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb20933b1194646087344f7b4994e0c24cac15ed","tid":669610,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6b9b992d3d2a803a69ee194da0c21d47257618","tid":669610,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:45:29.000Z","msg":"真係笑話，自圓其說。"},{"pid":"c1842f50d87a5639b6efe64a3c1268957279e718","tid":669610,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}